      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\" class=\"has-continuation\">For simplicity, we look at a homogeneous portfolio with identical pairwise correlations given by a single number in a simple lognormal model. For very high correlations, the basket behaves as a single assetâ€”thus removing assets has a small effect on</p>",
